{
  "text": "The main cluster I, in its order, was divided into six sub- This study showed that RAPD markers used successfully for identification and phylogenetic relationship among cultivars. [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] and [CITATION_3] indicated that RAPD analysis revealed high genomic polymorphism among pea (P. sativum L.) varieties. -104-",
